law.catch_line: Remedies additional to those available at law.
law.text: The provisions of KRS 224.30-100 to 224.30-190 are not exclusive, and the remedies provided for in KRS 224.30-100 to 224.30-190 shall be in addition to any other remedies provided for in any other law or available under common law.
law.history: Created 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 99, sec. 17, effective June 21, 1974.
